# CI/CD

## Platform

**gitlab-ci** — `.gitlab-ci.yml`



## Rules

1. All changes must pass CI before merging
2. Do not modify CI/CD configuration without team review
3. Keep build steps fast — cache dependencies where possible
4. Never commit secrets to CI configuration files
